00:37:46.310 --> 00:37:47.960
BARRY O'REILLY: Brilliant.

00:37:47.960 --> 00:37:52.000
Just to repeat the question,
typically in a Design Sprint

00:37:52.000 --> 00:37:54.880
within Google, we have
a specific challenge

00:37:54.880 --> 00:37:57.670
or question that we're
trying to answer.

00:37:57.670 --> 00:38:01.540
In ExecCamp, it sounds like
