that we advocate while we're

00:43:00.320 --> 00:43:01.570
running these things.

00:43:01.570 --> 00:43:03.410
And that's what makes
it so invigorating

00:43:03.410 --> 00:43:06.620
because no two
have been the same.

00:43:06.620 --> 00:43:09.140
We've got a high level
deliberate method,

00:43:09.140 --> 00:43:12.510
but the adaptability comes on
what we learn with each client

00:43:12.510 --> 00:43:13.620
when we do it.

00:43:13.620 --> 00:43:16.840
And we just pivot
the whole process

00:43:16.840 --> 00:43:20.580
to match what we're learning
as a team, which again, is very

00:43:20.580 --> 00:43:22.030
